info: Warby Parker Inc. designs, manufactures, and retails eyewear products for men and women. It offers eyeglasses, sunglasses, light-responsive lenses, blue-light-filtering lenses, and contact lenses, as well as eye exams and vision tests. As of June 30, 2021, it operated 145 retail stores, which included 142 locations in the United States and 3 locations in Canada, as well as online stores. The company was formerly known as JAND, Inc. and changed its name to Warby Parker Inc. in June 2021. Warby Parker Inc. was incorporated in 2009 and is headquartered in New York, New York.
